  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 3rd level, you have learned how to imbue yourself with the might of giants. As a bonus action, you magically gain the following benefits, which last for 1 minute:</p><ul><li>If you are smaller than Large, you become Large, along with anything you are wearing. If you lack the room to become Large, your size does not change.</li><li>You have advantage on Strength checks and Strength saving throws.</li><li>Once on each of your turns, one of your attacks with a weapon or an unarmed strike can deal an extra 1d6 damage to a target on a hit.</li></ul><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses of it when you finish a long rest.</p>",
